{"tid":1111580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜：上海、深圳可先實施民主","createTime":"2019-04-17T03:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T09:15:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":155,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"3941565937d4b72bfdced7d07f72d642d1e11c8d","tid":1111580,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜：上海、深圳可先實施民主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1555459885.A.0B6?fbclid=IwAR3YGdgvzfVYPT4mjk9uUHVUnWd6MW7-YCkURdsU_JS-Es20qA2-6Zy9Juw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoptt.tw%2Fp%2FGossiping.M.1555459885.A.0B6%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3YGdgvzfVYPT4mjk9uUHVUnWd6MW7-YCkURdsU_JS-Es20qA2-6Zy9Juw&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=6c8ae253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1555459885.A.0B6?fbclid=IwAR3YGdgvzfVYPT4mjk9uUHVUnWd6MW7-YCkURdsU_JS-Es20qA2-6Zy9Juw</a><br />\n<br />\n1.媒體來源:<br />\n東森<br />\n<br />\n2.記者署名<br />\n徐政璿、吳奕靖<br />\n<br />\n3.完整新聞標題:<br />\n與史丹佛學者會談 韓國瑜：上海、深圳可先實施民主<br />\n<br />\n4.完整新聞內文:<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜自10日起訪美9天，當地時間17日下午與媒體座談時透露，他在與美國駐阿富汗大使、哈佛大學教授艾江山（Karl Winfred Eikenberry）吃早餐時聊台灣選舉，他認為，大陸沿海城市像是上海或深圳可以仿照台灣的經驗，當國民所得達到1萬美金之後，說不定可以開始實施民主。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，台灣說實在比錢比不上人家，也不能跟人家比拳頭，最重要最美好的資源就所謂的Democracy（民主），「艾江山教授也一直對我們宣導民主，我也同時講說，也許有一天，當大陸某一個城市國民所得達到1萬時，說不定它有可能開始選舉議員，這就是台灣過去的經驗，在台北、高雄市長選舉之前先開放議員選舉，那國民所得到1萬美金的時候，整個城市居民的素質是不一樣的，所以我提出，例如上海、深圳到1萬美金之後，說不定大陸這方面也開始實施民主改革，那天來的時候，這個影響是非常巨大，簡單談到民主的問題是這樣子」。<br />\n<br />\n至於16日在史丹佛大學演講時，有將美國前總統甘迺迪的名言「不要問你的國家能為你做什麼，要問你能為你的國家做什麼」改寫成「不要問國家能為你做什麼; 要問你為這國家你把票投給了誰」。韓國瑜對此回應，民主政治就像佛家講的「種瓜得瓜，種豆得豆」因果關係，有幾流的人民，就會選出幾流的民意代表，有幾流民意代表，就會監督出幾流的政府，有幾流的政府，就有幾流的國家。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，所以一切回歸到民主最原始的點，當選民投票的時候，能不能夠選賢與能，投完了，人家拿到權力，表現能不能讓選民滿意，到最終還是要讓選民概括承受，舉這個例子是說，台灣鬼混20、30年，所有政治人物都是選民選出來的，能怪誰呢？所以下一次選舉「不要問國家能為你做什麼; 要問你為這國家你把票投給了誰」。<br />\n<br />\n針對美中台關係，韓國瑜說，他在史丹佛大學的演講中將台灣比喻成一位「美麗女孩」，皮膚好、眼睛大，美國、中國、日本都想追，難得集三千寵愛在一身，架構是這樣，那在這發展過程，可以每一方面都非常要好，去看電影，去喝咖啡去談戀愛，但不要隨便結婚，因為跟一個結婚另外一個就打死你，史丹佛所有師生聽到的都嚇一跳，因為沒有聽過這樣比喻，如果用很教條式，講完很僵硬，印象不鮮活，用這個例子舉出來，代表當前處境非常困難。<br />\n<br />\n5.完整新聞連結 (或短網址):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190417/1423921.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190417%2F1423921.htm&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=f622288b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190417/1423921.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n6.備註:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你以為你是誰啊，中國國家主席喔。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5ec7f9307d36b7b00cf56f80af6b127bb35bd3cd","tid":1111580,"uid":220701,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜咁撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e955ad582d019287dda5b1de265a57454d8c5bda","tid":1111580,"uid":32782,"like":30,"dislike":6,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"條友柒夠未 高雄市長學人咁大口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係當下當下當左自己係台灣總統？"},{"pid":"90dcbca60210565ac01d1380fc45af6f2c357749","tid":1111580,"uid":20241,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"係台灣9up開連條界係邊都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55766bf229be5f5192ee510ff857895e87631b8d","tid":1111580,"uid":76310,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"支持喎<br />\n<br />\n中共記住實施民主呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cde4e12cb8e6040b6dd81abc1d38da94cd4d69","tid":1111580,"uid":39365,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"口交部: 中國是最民主的國定, 全部代表都是人民選出來的, 主席也是由人民代表選出來的, 你看, 多民主"},{"pid":"16ae1f778cefec46d3e2a9d4b4d63a44fbd958fb","tid":1111580,"uid":62247,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"佢真係鳩up無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876de69e650de607b8c2b4ad5e4ac082b435accb","tid":1111580,"uid":33631,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489659944_0aba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489659944_0aba.jpg&h=ed164492&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac1fe6ab47362db5716ee3cba3090cd6ec0aa741","tid":1111580,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國已經有民主</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/34187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F34187.jpg&h=19186a7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a131a0011649b954e62ffd08ed70efb90db0cdf7","tid":1111580,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e955ad582d019287dda5b1de265a57454d8c5bda","tid":1111580,"uid":32782,"like":30,"dislike":6,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"條友柒夠未 高雄市長學人咁大口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係當下當下當左自己係台灣總統？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"佢直頭當自己中國國家主席添啦"},{"pid":"9dbb1f914971b1de0d55de5690a4d9a066d3eb17","tid":1111580,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"已經好民主啦"},{"pid":"5233c81439db131a8c326557186aa68fca6dd85f","tid":1111580,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9dbb1f914971b1de0d55de5690a4d9a066d3eb17","tid":1111580,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"已經好民主啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜統一中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfda471d0503e5c3bef61cccbb82e3f5d85a0725","tid":1111580,"uid":209097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:34:13.000Z","msg":"習下韓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cf7c1a6f8c369356c7ad0cfd09a94959691c3c","tid":1111580,"uid":190540,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"115c5e7f80eafb8635fc872c10b22983ace9b196","tid":1111580,"uid":109462,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實咪即係蔣經國三民主義統一中國嗰套，起碼唔係擁護中共體制嘅言論，唔明有乜嘢好抽秤；定係連登仔純粹慣性見到韓國瑜三隻字就要屌咗先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cec5f88e92b2719b22e6de4ef00c7e85378bca8","tid":1111580,"uid":109462,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔知唔知李登輝做總統嗰陣有樣嘢叫《國家統一綱領》，大概都係咁嘅內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><ins>肆、進程</ins></strong><br />\n一、 近程－－交流互惠階段<br />\n(一) 以交流促進瞭解，以互惠化解敵意；在交流中不危及對方的安全與安定，在互惠中不否定對方為政治實體，以建立良性互動關係。<br />\n(二) 建立兩岸交流秩序，制訂交流規範，設立中介機構，以維護兩岸人民權益；逐步放寬各項限制，擴大兩岸民間交流，以促進雙方社會繁榮。<br />\n(三) 在國家統一的目標下，為增進兩岸人民福祉：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸地區應積極推動經濟改革，逐步開放輿論，實行民主法治</span></strong>；台灣地區則應加速憲政改革，推動國家建設，建立均富社會。<br />\n(四) 兩岸應摒除敵對狀態，並在一個中國的原則下，以和平方式解決一切爭端，在國際間相互尊重，互不排斥，以利進入互信合作階段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80%E7%B6%B1%E9%A0%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B6%25B1%25E9%25A0%2598&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=b6c6038a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80%E7%B6%B1%E9%A0%98</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f2fa1f24e5a036d605e62a0cfdc2030f19d86446","tid":1111580,"uid":67151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"條友似真膠"},{"pid":"a1cee4b75392d924b99e1e27e73b8417b56a2efc","tid":1111580,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜一統中國，取代習近平。"},{"pid":"46af679328ee06d9c74115d609fd50be29c2ac8b","tid":1111580,"uid":137569,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"之前連登仔又話佢共諜<br />\n人哋依家講明國防要靠美國<br />\n唔俾面大陸<br />\n唔知連登仔又點講"},{"pid":"d550a2eeff44992573b732aeb5c2aa27e48499f2","tid":1111580,"uid":2949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"讓一部分人先自由起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eb33d58b7d226e7975bc11698adc3b820c3297","tid":1111580,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d674e0165ee7f5b79d868c05d3975790e085eb9","tid":1111580,"uid":165359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"同犯民班友一樣咁天真"},{"pid":"5717d6dd034915cde52b49a1fa69da3af12a025b","tid":1111580,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46af679328ee06d9c74115d609fd50be29c2ac8b","tid":1111580,"uid":137569,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"之前連登仔又話佢共諜<br />\n人哋依家講明國防要靠美國<br />\n唔俾面大陸<br />\n唔知連登仔又點講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"支那驚佢戇鳩自爆<br />\n咪寫稿踩下支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d00abb3a46f